A value enumeration that specifies the control pattern.

Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar" /> that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarAutomationPeer" />.

An object that supports the control pattern if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Scroll" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ItemContainer" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" /> value, or if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar" /> has items in the overflow menu and <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" /> value; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="patternInterface" />가 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Scroll" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ItemContainer" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" /> 값이거나 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar" />에 오버플로 메뉴의 항목이 있고 <paramref name="patternInterface" />가 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" /> 값인 경우 컨트롤 패턴을 지원하는 개체이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="null" />입니다.
